            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-1c615a33-b90d-46d5-ad58-cb92feb992d3">
                Mr. Kenneth Lindsay  (Combined English Universities)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-1c615a33-b90d-46d5-ad58-cb92feb992d3" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-03-31/debates/79b262be-2fa7-4c96-80f2-55b50ab1058b/NationalServiceBill#contribution-1c615a33-b90d-46d5-ad58-cb92feb992d3">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Has the Minister any idea of the spread as between the ages of 17½ and 26? For instance, does he imagine that 20 per cent. or 30 per cent. will opt at 17½?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1c615a33-b90d-46d5-ad58-cb92feb992d3" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-03-31/debates/79b262be-2fa7-4c96-80f2-55b50ab1058b/NationalServiceBill#contribution-1c615a33-b90d-46d5-ad58-cb92feb992d3">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
