    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-bef0f553-a427-47f6-aeee-ec6f7d81c179">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-bef0f553-a427-47f6-aeee-ec6f7d81c179">
                Mr. Stephen
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-bef0f553-a427-47f6-aeee-ec6f7d81c179" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-03-31/debates/79b262be-2fa7-4c96-80f2-55b50ab1058b/NationalServiceBill#contribution-bef0f553-a427-47f6-aeee-ec6f7d81c179">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The right hon. Gentleman said that if a person received a postponement right up to the age of 26, he might be called on after 26 for service. Up to what age? Might it be 30?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-bef0f553-a427-47f6-aeee-ec6f7d81c179" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-03-31/debates/79b262be-2fa7-4c96-80f2-55b50ab1058b/NationalServiceBill#contribution-bef0f553-a427-47f6-aeee-ec6f7d81c179">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-11f18ee1-9f29-4d5c-9ddc-784d063e7643">
