<p class="">Will the right hon. Gentleman allow me?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b7deecba-84f7-4b8d-80f8-520fe3cdd551" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
