            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-f9a3b459-8bdc-4124-895d-cbc3b004bf8a">
                Mr. K. Lindsay
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f9a3b459-8bdc-4124-895d-cbc3b004bf8a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
