            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-0f183f4e-6ed1-45cd-994e-2cc011ce9d40">
                Mrs. Paton
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-0f183f4e-6ed1-45cd-994e-2cc011ce9d40" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-03-31/debates/79b262be-2fa7-4c96-80f2-55b50ab1058b/NationalServiceBill#contribution-0f183f4e-6ed1-45cd-994e-2cc011ce9d40">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I said that it was in line with Conservative practice in the past.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-0f183f4e-6ed1-45cd-994e-2cc011ce9d40" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
