<p class="">The hon. Member should not carry on a sort of conversation across the Floor of the House. He should reserve his points until he makes a speech.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-173d962b-9a22-4b84-a9ba-15c77461ab7e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-03-31/debates/79b262be-2fa7-4c96-80f2-55b50ab1058b/NationalServiceBill#contribution-173d962b-9a22-4b84-a9ba-15c77461ab7e">
