<p class="">Only one out of five, then, under 25.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-8a27693b-7835-47bd-b6c9-6a4aa34d5bbf" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
