<p class="">That is hardly an answer to my question.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-3721db03-ff17-4ffe-8f1f-49ab6ee150b8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
